    {
      "heading": "题解",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>题目核心：</strong>物品 $i$ 做菜耗时 $c_i$。如果在时刻 $t$ 完成，这道菜的美味度为 $a_i - t \\cdot b_i$。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>开始推导：</strong>",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "假设在做这两道相邻的菜 $i$ 和 $j$ 之前，<strong>已经过去的时间是 $T$</strong>。",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>情况 1：先做菜</strong> $i$<strong>，后做菜</strong> $j$",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "做完 $i$ 时的时刻是 $T + c_i$。 $i$ 的美味度：$a_i - (T + c_i)b_i$",
          "depth": 3
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "做完 $j$ 时的时刻是 $T + c_i + c_j$。 $j$ 的美味度：$a_j - (T + c_i + c_j)b_j$",
          "depth": 3
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>总美味度 A</strong> = $a_i - Tb_i - c_ib_i \\quad + \\quad a_j - Tb_j - c_ib_j - c_jb_j$",
          "depth": 3
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>情况 2：先做菜</strong> $j$，<strong>后做菜</strong> $i$",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "做完 $j$ 时的时刻是 $T + c_j$。 $j$ 的美味度：$a_j - (T + c_j)b_j$",
          "depth": 3
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "做完 $i$ 时的时刻是 $T + c_j + c_i$。 $i$ 的美味度：$a_i - (T + c_j + c_i)b_i$",
          "depth": 3
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>总美味度 B</strong> = $a_j - Tb_j - c_jb_j \\quad + \\quad a_i - Tb_i - c_jb_i - c_ib_i$",
          "depth": 3
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>列不等式：</strong>",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "我们希望<strong>先做 $i$ 后做 $j$ 更优</strong>，所以令：<strong>总美味度 A > 总美味度 B</strong>",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "math",
          "latex": "$$a_i - Tb_i - c_ib_i + a_j - Tb_j - c_ib_j - c_jb_j > a_j - Tb_j - c_jb_j + a_i - Tb_i - c_jb_i - c_ib_i$$",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>暴力化简（消消乐时间）：</strong>",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "两边都有 $a_i, a_j, -Tb_i, -Tb_j, -c_ib_i, -c_jb_j$，统统划掉！",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "最后竟然只剩下极其干净的两项：",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "math",
          "latex": "$$-c_ib_j > -c_jb_i$$",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "两边同乘 $-1$（记得变号）：",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "math",
          "latex": "$$\\mathbf{c_i \\cdot b_j < c_j \\cdot b_i}$$",
          "depth": 2
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "代码",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "code",
          "lang": "cpp",
          "code": "struct node {\n\tll a, b, c;\n};\nll dp[N];\nvoid solve(int CASE)\n{\n\tint t, n; cin >> t >> n;\n\tvar p = vector<node>(n + 1);\n\tfa(i, 1, n)cin >> p[i].a;\n\tfa(i, 1, n)cin >> p[i].b;\n\tfa(i, 1, n)cin >> p[i].c;\n\tsort(all1(p), [](const node& a, const node& b)->bool {\n\t\treturn a.c * b.b < b.c * a.b;\n\t\t});\n\tll ans = 0;\n\tfa(i, 1, n) {\n\t\tconst var& [a, b, c] = p[i];\n\t\tfb(j, t, c) {\n\t\t\tdp[j] = max(dp[j], dp[j - c] + a - j * b);\n\t\t\tans = max(ans, dp[j]);\n\t\t}\n\t}\n\tcout << ans << endl;\n\treturn;\n}",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
